Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你确定？\N{\fs40}You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:18.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他亲眼所见 陛下\N{\fs40}With his own eyes, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:32.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,呆在这里 不要告诉任何人\N{\fs40}Stay here. Tell no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,帮我更衣\N{\fs40}Help me dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都谁知道了？\N{\fs40}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的侍女 塔雅\N{\fs40}My handmaiden, Talya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:00.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一些仆人\N{\fs40}Some of the servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:07.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当我昨晚见到他……\N{\fs40}I saw him last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在他还没——\N{\fs40}before he--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他告诉我他想立伊耿为王\N{\fs40}He told me he wished for Aegon to be king.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:27.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,千真万确\N{\fs40}It is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:30.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他亲口所说\N{\fs40}Uttered with his own lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:33.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他对我说了遗言 我是唯一听到的\N{\fs40}His last words to me and I was the only one to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在他死了\N{\fs40}And now he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么事急成这样？\N{\fs40}What is it that could not have waited an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:11.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,多恩打起来了？\N{\fs40}Was Dorne invaded?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王死了\N{\fs40}The King is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:29.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们哀悼“安宁王”韦赛里斯……\N{\fs40}We grieve for Viserys the Peaceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:32.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哀悼我们的国王……\N{\fs40}our sovereign...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哀悼我们的朋友\N{\fs40}our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但他给我们留了一个礼物\N{\fs40}But he has left us a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:49.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他用最后一口气 向王后诉出了遗愿：\N{\fs40}With his last breath, he impressed upon the Queen his final wish:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他的儿子 伊耿……\N{\fs40}that his son, Aegon...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:56.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,应当继位为七国之主\N{\fs40}should succeed him as Lord of the Seven Kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:08.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,既然他有此遗愿 我们也可以安心\N{\fs40}Then we may proceed now with the full assurance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:10.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,继续长久以来的计划\N{\fs40}of his blessing on our long-laid plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的 有很多事情要做\N{\fs40}Yes. There is much to be done,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:14.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如我们之前所讨论的\N{\fs40}as we've previously discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都城守备队队长中有两位\N{\fs40}Now, there are two among the captains
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:19.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,依旧忠诚于戴蒙\N{\fs40}of the City Watch that remain loyal to Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:21.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把他们换掉\N{\fs40}Let us replace them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,兰尼斯特大人？\N{\fs40}Lord Lannister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国库在掌控之中\N{\fs40}The Treasury is well in hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:25.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,出于安全考虑 金子将会分开保存\N{\fs40}The gold will be divided for safekeeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:28.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,向我们的盟友 奔流城和高庭 送去渡鸦\N{\fs40}Let ravens be sent to our allies, Riverrun and Highgarden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如我理解无误 御前会议的成员\N{\fs40}Am I to understand that members of the small council
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:34.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一直都瞒着我 密谋把我儿子推上王座？\N{\fs40}have been planning secretly to install my son without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:39.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没必要让你沾染阴谋 王后陛下\N{\fs40}My Queen, there was no need to sully you with darkling schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:40.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不同意\N{\fs40}I will not have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:43.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,亲耳听到你们竟然在密谋\N{\fs40}To hear that you are plotting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:46.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要顶替掉国王选定的继承人！\N{\fs40}to replace the King's chosen heir with an imposter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:48.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王的长子不能算是顶替者\N{\fs40}His firstborn son is hardly an imposter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:52.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有数百名领主大人和有产骑士向对公主宣誓效忠\N{\fs40}Hundreds of lords and landed knights swore fealty to the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.37,0:06:54.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是差不多20年前的事 大多数人如今都死了\N{\fs40}That was some 20 years ago. Most of them now dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:55.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你听到国王之手大人的话了\N{\fs40}You heard the Lord Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:57.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无论密谋与否 国王改变他的主意了\N{\fs40}Plot or no, the King changed his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:01.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我如今七十有六\N{\fs40}I am six-and-seventy years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:06.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我认识韦赛里斯的时间比在座的各位都要长\N{\fs40}I have known Viserys longer than any who sit at this table.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:10.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我绝不会相信他在病榻上独身一人的时候 说出了这种话\N{\fs40}And I will not believe that he said this on his deathbed, alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:13.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只有那孩子的母亲作证\N{\fs40}with only the boy's mother as a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是强夺！\N{\fs40}This is seizure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:19.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是偷窃！这是叛国！\N{\fs40}It is theft! It is treason!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:20.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这起码是——\N{\fs40}At the least, it is--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:22.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,注意你说的话 林曼\N{\fs40}Mind your tongue, Lyman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王昨晚还好好的……\N{\fs40}The King was well last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:27.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大家都见到了\N{\fs40}by all accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:33.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在座的哪位敢发誓 他是自然死亡的？\N{\fs40}Which of you here can swear that he died of his own accord?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:37.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,毕斯柏里伯爵 你在指控在座的哪位弑君？\N{\fs40}Which of us are you accusing of regicide, Lord Beesbury?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:41.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不关心是你们哪一位 还是集体谋划的\N{\fs40}Whether it was one of you, or all of you, I care not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我绝不会参与——\N{\fs40}I will have no part--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:44.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坐下！\N{\fs40}Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:46.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.01,0:08:01.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,扔掉剑 脱下你的白袍 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}Throw down your sword and remove your cloak, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:06.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是你的队长 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}I am your Lord Commander, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把剑扔了\N{\fs40}Cast down your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:11.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我无法忍受王后陛下遭受冒犯\N{\fs40}I will not suffer insults to Her Grace the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:14.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我没被冒犯 克里斯顿爵士 你—— 把剑放下\N{\fs40}There was no insult to me, Ser Criston. Y-- Put aside your blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:23.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有必要这样么？\N{\fs40}Has it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,队长 够了\N{\fs40}Lord Commander, enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把毕斯柏里伯爵搬走吧\N{\fs40}Let us have Lord Beesbury removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:32.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs40}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在我们完事之前 大门必须紧闭\N{\fs40}The door remains shut until we finish our business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,风息堡是个问题\N{\fs40}Storm's End is of concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:59.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们不知道博洛斯公爵是否忠于我们\N{\fs40}We may not assume the loyalty of Lord Borros.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:01.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是他有四个女儿 全部未婚\N{\fs40}But he has four daughters, all of them unmarried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,合适的婚配——\N{\fs40}The right proposal--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉怎么办？\N{\fs40}What of Rhaenyra?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.12,0:09:08.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然不能放前任继承人自由\N{\fs40}The former heir cannot, of course, be allowed to remain free
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:11.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为她的主张去拉拢支持\N{\fs40}and draw support to her claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:14.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的意思是要囚禁她\N{\fs40}You mean to imprison her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:16.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她和她的家人将有机会\N{\fs40}She and her family will be given the opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:20.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,向新国王公开宣誓服从\N{\fs40}to publicly swear obeisance to the new King.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她绝不会屈膝臣服\N{\fs40}She will never bend the knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙也不会 你懂他的\N{\fs40}Nor will Daemon, which you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你打算杀掉他们\N{\fs40}You plan to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而且在座的都同意\N{\fs40}And all here accede to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.82,0:09:41.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您的父亲是正确的 陛下\N{\fs40}Your father is correct, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:44.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个活着的挑战者会带来战争与杀戮\N{\fs40}A living challenger invites battle and bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:47.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是 这当然不光彩\N{\fs40}It is unsavory, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:51.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但这是为了伊耿继位做出的必要牺牲\N{\fs40}But a sacrifice we must make to secure Aegon's succession.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而且还要考虑到戴蒙\N{\fs40}And then there is Daemon to consider.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王当然不希望任何不光彩的——\N{\fs40}The King wouldn't wish for any unsavory--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:55.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但国王绝不会想要……\N{\fs40}But the King did not wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他女儿被谋杀！\N{\fs40}for the murder of his daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他爱她 我不允许你否认这点\N{\fs40}He loved her. I will not have you deny this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:01.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但——\N{\fs40}And yet--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:03.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,再多说一个字 我就把你赶出房间\N{\fs40}One more word and I will have you removed from this chamber 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:04.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,发配长城！\N{\fs40}and sent to the Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:18.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您有何建议 陛下？\N{\fs40}What do you suggest, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:23.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,时间宝贵\N{\fs40}Time is of the essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,维斯特林队长……\N{\fs40}Lord Commander Westerling...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.26,0:10:38.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,带着你的骑士们去龙石岛\N{\fs40}take your knights to Dragonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:40.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要干净利落\N{\fs40}Be quick and be clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:57.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是御林铁卫队长\N{\fs40}I am Lord Commander of the Kingsguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,除了国王我谁也不认\N{\fs40}I recognize no authority but the King's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:06.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在还没有国王……\N{\fs40}And until there is one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:10.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这里也就没有我的位置\N{\fs40}I have no place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:26.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想 我们的宿命就是渴求别人所拥有的\N{\fs40}It is our fate, I think, to crave always what is given to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:31.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果一个人拥有一样东西 另一个人就会将之夺去\N{\fs40}If one possesses a thing, the other will take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的 公主\N{\fs40}Yes, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:38.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿去哪了？\N{\fs40}Where is Aegon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不在这啊\N{\fs40}Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他怎么没在自己房间里\N{\fs40}He's not in his rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\fs40}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N{\fs40}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:21.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你父亲他... - 木板底 凶兽倚\N{\fs40}-Your father-- -There is a beast beneath the boards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:24.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哦 我亲爱的\N{\fs40}Oh, my dearest love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊利克爵士\N{\fs40}Ser Erryk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:52.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王子去哪了？\N{\fs40}Where's the Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:55.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,首相大人恕罪 我不知道\N{\fs40}Forgive me, Lord Hand. I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你发誓保护他\N{\fs40}But you're sworn to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:12:59.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他下了命令 让我必须离开\N{\fs40}He exploits his authority to order me away,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:01.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,又躲着不让我找到 大人\N{\fs40}and then he evades me, my Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:08.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他大概已经偷偷离开红堡\N{\fs40}I believe he may have left the Keep secretly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:10.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,混进了城里\N{\fs40}gone into the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:12.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去找他\N{\fs40}Find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只带上你哥哥\N{\fs40}Take no one else but your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把白袍脱了\N{\fs40}And remove your white cloaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别让人知道你们是谁 在找什么……\N{\fs40}None can know who you are or what you seek...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后也不行\N{\fs40}including the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,遵命 大人\N{\fs40}My Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,直接带他来单独见我 伊利克爵士\N{\fs40}Bring him to me, and me alone, Ser Erryk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:52.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是干什么？\N{\fs40}What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,卫兵 卫兵！\N{\fs40}Guard. Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:32.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,红堡里没有伊耿王子的踪迹 陛下\N{\fs40}Prince Aegon's not to be found within the castle walls, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您父亲已经派伊利克爵士去城里找他了\N{\fs40}Your father has sent Ser Erryk into the city to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:40.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊利克爵士了解伊耿 他有优势\N{\fs40}Ser Erryk knows Aegon. He has the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:51.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会再次相信你和你的忠诚 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs40}I trust again to you, Ser Criston, and to your loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.05,0:14:54.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,必须找到伊耿 带他来见我\N{\fs40}Aegon must be found, and he must be brought to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,事关七国的命运\N{\fs40}The very fate of the Seven Kingdoms depends on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:02.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看在你对我 对你的王后的情分上\N{\fs40}Everything you feel for me as your Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不会让您失望\N{\fs40}I will not fail you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.78,0:15:09.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我和你一起去\N{\fs40}I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:12.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不能去 伊蒙德\N{\fs40}That would not be my desire, Aemond.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:14.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,万一出了什么事——\N{\fs40}If anything has happened--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:17.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科尔需要我 母亲\N{\fs40}Cole needs me, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:20.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,了解伊耿习性的 不只伊利克爵士一个人\N{\fs40}Ser Erryk isn't the only one who knows Aegon's doings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:50.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在我第十三个命名日那天 伊耿带我来了丝绸街\N{\fs40}Aegon brought me to the Street of Silk on my thirteenth name day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:53.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他说这是作哥哥的职责\N{\fs40}It was his duty as my brother, he said,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,确保我像他一样受过教导\N{\fs40}to ensure I was as educated as he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:03.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,至少我是这么理解的\N{\fs40}At least that's what I understood him to mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.17,0:16:07.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我没明白\N{\fs40}I don't follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他说“是时候滋润一下那话儿了”\N{\fs40}He said, “Time to get it wet.”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:14.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,每个女人都是圣母的化身 不能说这种亵渎的话\N{\fs40}Every woman is an image of the Mother, to be spoken of with reverence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:28.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,昨晚 我们有位酒友不知去向\N{\fs40}Sometime last night, we...misplaced our drinking companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:31.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们知道他过去经常来照顾你们的生意\N{\fs40}Knowing that he has been, in the past, a patron of your fine establishment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:33.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就想着来打听他的下落\N{\fs40}we thought to inquire here as to his whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他长什么样\N{\fs40}And describe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这件事很敏感\N{\fs40}That is a delicate matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:43.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,跟你直说吧 我们在找年轻的伊耿王子\N{\fs40}You see, the man we seek is the young Prince Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:46.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,希望你们干这一行的口风不会让我失望\N{\fs40}I may trust, I hope, in the discretion of your trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:49.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王子不在这\N{\fs40}The Prince is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:54.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那他来过吗？或许早些时候？\N{\fs40}Has he been here? Earlier, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:57.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那可太早了 上次来是几年前了\N{\fs40}Quite a bit earlier. Years ago, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:58.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最近呢？\N{\fs40}But more recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:03.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他不常来丝绸街\N{\fs40}He does not frequent the Street of Silk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:06.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,众所周知 他的品味.……\N{\fs40}His tastes are known to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没那么讲究\N{\fs40}less discriminating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:11.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么意思？\N{\fs40}Meaning what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:17.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,祝你好运 好爵士 祝你朋友更加好运\N{\fs40}I wish you luck, good Ser. And my best to your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你都长这么大了\N{\fs40}How you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯修改了遗愿\N{\fs40}Viserys amended his wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就这么简单\N{\fs40}It's as simple as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们曾宣誓效忠雷妮拉\N{\fs40}You once swore your banners to Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.06,0:17:46.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在 你们必须宣誓效忠未来的国王\N{\fs40}You must now pledge them to the future king.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:57.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,事关重大 我得先和我的族人商议\N{\fs40}I must confer first with my house on this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:02.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不明表立场 你就不能走出这个房间\N{\fs40}You'll not leave this room without declaring your intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:14.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不做背誓者\N{\fs40}I am no oath breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.42,0:18:19.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不会屈膝\N{\fs40}I will not bend the knee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:29.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有谁？\N{\fs40}Anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:45.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,费尔家族将继续效忠公主\N{\fs40}House Fell keeps its sworn oath to the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:50.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs40}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:11.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王万岁\N{\fs40}Long live the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:13.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王万岁\N{\fs40}Long live the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:48.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看来你也不怎么了解伊耿的喜好啊\N{\fs40}It seems you were mistaken as to Aegon's habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.72,0:19:51.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他可能已经被雇佣兵抓走\N{\fs40}He could be in the hands of mercenaries,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,跟着船去夷地了\N{\fs40}on a ship to Yi Ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:55.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也可能已经死了\N{\fs40}He could be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:58.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看在你母亲份上 但愿不会那样\N{\fs40}Let us hope, for your mother's sake, that is not the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:15.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,咱来看看\N{\fs40}Let's have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:18.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 去吧 - 过来 过来！\N{\fs40}-Go on. -Come here. Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:19.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,给我上去 你个小——\N{\fs40}Get in there, you little--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.64,0:20:28.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,耶！\N{\fs40}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:30.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,上啊！\N{\fs40}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们多大？\N{\fs40}How old are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.07,0:20:44.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,十岁左右吧\N{\fs40}About 10 years, I should say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:47.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这些人让孩子们蓄指甲 磨尖牙\N{\fs40}They have them grow their nails and file the teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,好让他们更难对付\N{\fs40}Makes them more formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:51.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,上啊！\N{\fs40}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:54.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿王子在这度过了许多个夜晚\N{\fs40}Prince Aegon spends many a night in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:56.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在你知道他是什么德行了？\N{\fs40}Do you see now what he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:58.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你还没看到他的全部呢\N{\fs40}You've not seen everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:07.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿的种?\N{\fs40}Aegon's?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我打赌 只是其中之一\N{\fs40}One of many, I'd wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:30.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我这么一个训练有素的战士 在城里四处搜寻\N{\fs40}Here I am, trawling the city, ever the good soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:34.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那个对自己与生俱来的权利毫不关心的废物\N{\fs40}in search of a wastrel who's never taken half an interest in his birthright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:39.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,认真学历史 学哲学的人是身为次子的我\N{\fs40}'Tis I the younger brother who studies history and philosophy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:40.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,努力练剑的人是我\N{\fs40}it is I who trains with the sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:42.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,骑乘世界上最大的龙 那也是我\N{\fs40}who rides the largest dragon in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我才是那个应该——\N{\fs40}It is I who should be--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:51.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别人轻松得到 我们却得努力去争取 我知道那种滋味\N{\fs40}I know what it is to toil for what others are freely given.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:56.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们是找不到他的 科尔\N{\fs40}And we can't find him, Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:22:00.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是个不愿堕落的体面人\N{\fs40}You are a decent man with no taste for depravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:02.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他有自己的秘密……\N{\fs40}His secrets are his own...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.69,0:22:04.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就让他留着秘密吧\N{\fs40}and he's welcome to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.19,0:22:06.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是铁王座的下一顺位继承人\N{\fs40}I'm next in line to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.07,0:22:09.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果他们来找我\N{\fs40}Should they come looking for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.45,0:22:11.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不会躲起来\N{\fs40}I intend to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:24.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,必须做点什么 伊耿不适合做统治者\N{\fs40}Something must be done. Aegon is unfit to rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:26.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你都已经容忍王子的癖好这么多年了\N{\fs40}You tolerated the Prince's proclivities for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:27.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只因这是我的誓言职责 亚历克\N{\fs40}Because it was my sworn duty, Arryk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.05,0:22:29.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,把动脑子的事留给首相吧\N{\fs40}It's for the Hand to find wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:32.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们只要至死服从发过的誓言就好\N{\fs40}We swore an oath of service until death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:34.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,打扰一下 佬爷\N{\fs40}A moment of your time, m'lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.39,0:22:38.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们可不是你的顾客\N{\fs40}You'll find no buyers for your wares here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.69,0:22:43.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可以带你们去见伊耿王子\N{\fs40}I can take you to Prince Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.03,0:22:48.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或者说 有个知道王子在哪里的人派我过来\N{\fs40}Rather, I am sent by one who knows where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.28,0:22:50.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那人会告诉你们 但要收钱\N{\fs40}Who'll tell you, for a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:54.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,带他过来 我们再聊聊价钱\N{\fs40}Deliver him, and we'll consider your price.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.45,0:22:59.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们夫人可不跟红堡里的仆从打交道……\N{\fs40}My mistress will not treat with the servants of the Keep...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:01.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,虽然你们也很高贵\N{\fs40}exalted though they may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.46,0:23:04.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但她只信任国王之手\N{\fs40}She'll trust this to the Hand of the King only.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:06.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不可能\N{\fs40}Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.71,0:23:10.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我相信他会想听听白蛆要告诉他什么\N{\fs40}I think he will wish to hear what the White Worm can tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.90,0:23:28.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,停！别开门！\N{\fs40}Halt! Hold the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.82,0:23:33.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,放开我！\N{\fs40}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:34.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他准备从大门出逃\N{\fs40}He was fleeing from the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.87,0:23:36.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们知道我是谁吗?\N{\fs40}Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.12,0:23:38.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我打赌是要给公主送信\N{\fs40}A warning for the Princess, I'd wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.50,0:23:41.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你怎么说?\N{\fs40}What say you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:45.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,御前审问长想多了\N{\fs40}The Lord Confessor presumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:49.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我对公主没有偏爱\N{\fs40}I have no love for the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.97,0:23:53.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那你急急忙忙要去哪里?\N{\fs40}And where were you going then with such urgency?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.14,0:24:01.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让御前执法官带下去吧\N{\fs40}Let the King's Justice take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.48,0:24:07.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,放开我！\N{\fs40}Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:10.24,Note_top,,0,0,0,,不！这是不对的！\N{\fs32}No! This is not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.36,0:24:10.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你做得很好 拉里斯大人\N{\fs40}You did well, Lord Larys.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:13.11,Note_top,,0,0,0,,我一定会——\N{\fs32}I will--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.32,0:24:13.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,尽我的职责罢了 首相大人\N{\fs40}Only my duty, my Lord Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.20,0:24:15.09,Note_top,,0,0,0,,你以为你是谁？\N{\fs32}Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.57,0:24:16.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你最近和王后待在一起的时间很长\N{\fs40}You've spent many hours with the Queen of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.58,0:24:27.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这些时间或许终究会让您受益\N{\fs40}There's no reason those hours could not, in the end, benefit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.59,0:26:00.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,出于礼貌 我愿意假定\N{\fs40}I will do you the considerable courtesy of assuming
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.93,0:26:04.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我今早在这里受到的冒犯有个合理的原因\N{\fs40}there is a good reason for the outrage of my treatment here this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.39,0:26:09.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我为失礼表示诚挚的歉意\N{\fs40}My sincerest regrets for the lack of ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.98,0:26:13.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王……\N{\fs40}The King.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.24,0:26:21.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而你在谋划篡夺王位\N{\fs40}And you are usurping the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.12,0:26:22.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是我夫君临终的遗愿\N{\fs40}It was my husband's dying wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.08,0:26:26.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不管你信不信都无关紧要\N{\fs40}Believe it or no, it is of no consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.87,0:26:28.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿将会成为国王\N{\fs40}Aegon will be king.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.84,0:26:33.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我来这里是想让你支持我\N{\fs40}I came here to ask your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.59,0:26:37.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我得赞赏你的胆量\N{\fs40}Well, I must credit you for your boldness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.09,0:26:41.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦列利安家族早就跟雷妮拉公主结盟了\N{\fs40}House Velaryon has long allied itself with the Princess Rhaenyra 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.55,0:26:43.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你得到了什么?\N{\fs40}and what has it gained you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.68,0:26:47.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你女儿孤零零地……死在潘托斯\N{\fs40}Your daughter dead... alone in Pentos.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.85,0:26:50.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你儿子被戴绿帽\N{\fs40}Your son cuckolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.81,0:26:53.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉的继承人都不是你们家族的后代\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra's heirs are none of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.61,0:26:58.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是你丈夫如此轻率地想要攫取王座\N{\fs40}It is your husband who grasps so heedlessly for the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.49,0:27:01.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他甚至也抛弃了你\N{\fs40}And even he has abandoned you:
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.24,0:27:03.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,孤注一掷地打了六年仗\N{\fs40}gone these six long years to fight a desperate battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.99,0:27:07.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,回来时身受重伤 或许是致命伤\N{\fs40}returning grievously, if not mortally, wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.16,0:27:09.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,留下潮头岛夫人独自规划航线\N{\fs40}leaving the Lady of Driftmark to chart her course alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.63,0:27:15.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们家的族语可不是反复无常\N{\fs40}The word of my house is not fickle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.59,0:27:20.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道不会 但是 亲爱的堂姐……\N{\fs40}No. But, dear cousin...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.47,0:27:26.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你比当今世上任何人都更明白我现在说的话\N{\fs40}you more than any soul alive understand what I say now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.77,0:27:31.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮丝公主 我很爱我的夫君 但我必须说出我们都知道的事实\N{\fs40}Princess Rhaenys, I loved my husband, but I will speak the truth we both know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.19,0:27:33.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你本该是女王\N{\fs40}You should've been queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.27,0:27:38.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可没想过能听到你这么说\N{\fs40}I little thought to hear those words from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.53,0:27:41.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无论血脉还是气质 铁王座都应该是你的\N{\fs40}The Iron Throne was yours by blood and by temperament.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.45,0:27:44.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯本可以做个乡下领主\N{\fs40}Viserys would've lived his days a country lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.16,0:27:46.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,狩猎 研究他那些历史 满足地过完一生\N{\fs40}content to hunt and study his histories,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.28,0:27:48.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但是……事已至此\N{\fs40}but... here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.83,0:27:54.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们不能统治 但我们可以指导男人统治\N{\fs40}We do not rule but we may guide the men that do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.21,0:27:56.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,柔和地……\N{\fs40}Gently...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.96,0:28:00.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,远离暴力和毁灭 让国家走向和平\N{\fs40}away from violence and sure destruction and instead toward peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.22,0:28:05.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你把我关在这里是为了和平吗?\N{\fs40}Is it in the name of peace that you've imprisoned me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.39,0:28:06.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的龙怎么办? \N{\fs40}And what of my dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.90,0:28:07.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我们处于劣势\N{\fs40}If we are overmatched,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.64,0:28:10.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉一定会袭击我们 随后就是战争\N{\fs40}Rhaenyra will be tempted to strike us, and war will ensue.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.02,0:28:15.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果没有你的龙 我们或许可以说服她谈判\N{\fs40}Without your dragon, she may be persuaded to negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.61,0:28:20.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你想要潮头岛 它就是你的\N{\fs40}If it's Driftmark you want, you shall have it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.65,0:28:24.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,给你和你的外孙女 或传给你中意的人选\N{\fs40}for you and your granddaughters to pass on as you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.95,0:28:31.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你比我想象中聪明\N{\fs40}You are wiser than I believed you to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.87,0:28:36.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,阿莉森·海塔尔\N{\fs40}Alicent Hightower.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.29,0:28:40.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真正的王后会为子民权衡得失\N{\fs40}A true queen counts the cost to her people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.05,0:28:45.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可你还在为男人劳碌\N{\fs40}And yet you toil still in service to men.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.76,0:28:48.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你父亲 你丈夫 你儿子\N{\fs40}Your father, your husband, your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.52,0:28:52.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你渴望的不是自由\N{\fs40}You desire not to be free,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.18,0:28:55.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而是在你监牢的墙上开一扇窗\N{\fs40}but to make a window in the wall of your prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.52,0:28:59.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你从来都没想过自己……\N{\fs40}Have you never imagined yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.86,0:29:01.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坐上铁王座吗?\N{\fs40}on the Iron Throne?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.12,0:29:16.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在这好好想想吧\N{\fs40}I'll leave you with your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.88,0:29:20.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,想好了就摇铃\N{\fs40}Ring the bell when you have an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.32,0:29:46.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,殿下你瞧\N{\fs40}My Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.71,0:30:00.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想你就是神秘的白蛆吧\N{\fs40}You yourself are the mysterious White Worm, I take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.21,0:30:06.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或者你也只不过是这颗臭洋葱上剥下的又一层皮？\N{\fs40}Or are you simply a further peel in this stinking onion?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.01,0:30:10.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我为国王的驾崩致哀\N{\fs40}My condolences on the passing of your king.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.99,0:30:27.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿王子在哪儿？\N{\fs40}Where is Prince Aegon?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.03,0:30:34.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我想 王子正在跳蚤窝呢 那儿的人可没法信任\N{\fs40}I thought, the Prince is in Flea Bottom where no one is to be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.16,0:30:39.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我最好把他偷偷藏在一个安全的地方……免得有人来找他\N{\fs40}I'd best secrete him somewhere safe... in case they come looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.46,0:30:41.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王子在哪儿？\N{\fs40}Where's the Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.63,0:30:44.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他已经被安全地藏起来了\N{\fs40}He is safely tucked away.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.51,0:30:51.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望停止对跳蚤窝孩子们的野蛮奴役\N{\fs40}I want an end to the savage use of children in Flea Bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.30,0:30:54.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们被迫相互厮杀 甚至更糟……\N{\fs40}They are forced to fight, and worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.68,0:30:58.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你那些金袍子收了贿赂 对此视而不见\N{\fs40}your gold cloaks take the bribes given them to look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.52,0:31:05.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而朝廷对这种无耻之行不是纵容就是无视\N{\fs40}An obscenity either tolerated or ignored by the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.65,0:31:09.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会关注此事\N{\fs40}I'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.70,0:31:11.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我向你保证\N{\fs40}You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.62,0:31:18.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,等你的计谋得逞\N{\fs40}When your plots ripen
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.37,0:31:22.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,外孙登上王位之时\N{\fs40}and you install your grandson on the throne,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.63,0:31:25.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,记住 那都是源于我的扶持\N{\fs40}remember it was me who put him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.88,0:31:30.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要是想杀他 容易得就像拍死水果上的黄蜂\N{\fs40}I could have killed him as easily as a wasp on fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.13,0:31:35.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没有民众的支持 你们哪来的权力\N{\fs40}There is no power but what the people allow you to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.72,0:31:39.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我会记住的\N{\fs40}I will remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.04,0:32:05.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,听着\N{\fs40}Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.76,0:32:15.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不……不！\N{\fs40}No... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.55,0:32:17.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs40}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.15,0:32:28.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,白蛆在哪儿？\N{\fs40}Where is the White Worm?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.40,0:32:29.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她把你卖了个好价钱\N{\fs40}She sold you for a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.82,0:32:31.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你们凭啥给她钱？\N{\fs40}And why have you paid it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.11,0:32:35.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要见我妈\N{\fs40}I want my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.87,0:32:39.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的外公 国王之手 在城外等你\N{\fs40}Your grandfather, the Hand, will meet you outside the city walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.67,0:32:49.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他人拼死而不得的东西你却不想要 伊耿\N{\fs40}You flee what other men die seeking, Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.85,0:33:08.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真是遗憾 朋友\N{\fs40}I do regret this, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.93,0:33:41.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不要！住手！不要\N{\fs40}No! Stop! No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.02,0:33:48.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我巴不得你消失呢\N{\fs40}I was hoping you disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.04,0:33:48.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,咱爸真死了？\N{\fs40}Is our father truly dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.06,0:33:52.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,对……而且他们打算让你当国王\N{\fs40}Yes... and they're going to make you king.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.19,0:33:56.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 不要！- 你到底帮不帮忙？！\N{\fs40}-No! -Are you going to help me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.99,0:34:01.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不要！放开我！\N{\fs40}No! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.45,0:34:02.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你兄弟呢？\N{\fs40}Where's your brother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.58,0:34:05.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,放开我！\N{\fs40}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.25,0:34:07.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,弟弟！\N{\fs40}Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.71,0:34:16.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,放开我！\N{\fs40}Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.43,0:34:18.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不想统治！\N{\fs40}I have no wish to rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.05,0:34:21.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也没责任感！我根本不合适\N{\fs40}No taste for duty! I'm not suited.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.80,0:34:23.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这点我倒是不反对\N{\fs40}You'll get no argument from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.14,0:34:26.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,放我走吧 我会找艘船 远走高飞\N{\fs40}You let me go, I will find a ship and sail away,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.06,0:34:28.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,永远消失\N{\fs40}never to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.15,0:34:33.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后正等着呢\N{\fs40}The Queen awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.56,0:35:05.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这步棋走得好\N{\fs40}Well played.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.36,0:35:07.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这可不是游戏\N{\fs40}None of this is a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.89,0:35:10.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你依然把它当成游戏\N{\fs40}And yet you treat it as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.23,0:35:12.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一场激动人心的竞赛\N{\fs40}A charming contest,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.81,0:35:16.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,奖品是一袋银币\N{\fs40}the prize, a pouch of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.53,0:35:23.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们相互倚仗这么多年\N{\fs40}We have relied on one another these many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.78,0:35:27.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在正是争取家族利益的时机 这是我们共同的期望\N{\fs40}And now it is the good of the family that we both desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.66,0:35:31.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无论有何分歧 我们总是一条心\N{\fs40}Whatever our differences, our hearts remain as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.96,0:35:35.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们从来不是一条心\N{\fs40}Our hearts were never one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.88,0:35:37.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我现在明白了\N{\fs40}I see that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.63,0:35:40.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不过是你的一枚棋子罢了\N{\fs40}Rather, I have been a piece that you moved about the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.34,0:35:44.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,若真如此 我还让你成为了七大王国的王后\N{\fs40}If that is true, then I made you Queen of the Seven Kingdoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.85,0:35:47.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不也想要吗？\N{\fs40}Would you have desired it otherwise?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.21,0:35:49.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我怎么知道？\N{\fs40}How could I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.23,0:35:53.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的想法都是你灌输的\N{\fs40}I wanted whatever you impressed upon me to want.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.56,0:35:56.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在要还债了\N{\fs40}And now the debt comes due.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.32,0:35:59.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你过去很乐于还的债\N{\fs40}A debt you were happy enough to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.20,0:36:00.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是牺牲\N{\fs40}A sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.11,0:36:04.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为了王国稳定而做出的牺牲\N{\fs40}A sacrifice made for the stability of the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.99,0:36:07.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还没有哪个国王不会为了保护多数人\N{\fs40}No king has ever lived that hasn't had to forfeit
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.29,0:36:09.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而牺牲少数人\N{\fs40}the lives of a few to protect the many.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.45,0:36:11.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不过我理解你的道德洁癖\N{\fs40}Though I understand your squeamishness.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.66,0:36:15.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不愿杀人不是弱点！\N{\fs40}Reluctance to murder is not a weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.01,0:36:20.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿在我手上\N{\fs40}I have Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.76,0:36:22.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,之后怎么办 由我决定\N{\fs40}We'll proceed now as I see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.35,0:36:32.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们给龙石岛的雷妮拉开出条件\N{\fs40}We will send terms to Rhaenyra on Dragonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.56,0:36:35.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真诚的条件 这样她才能体面地接受\N{\fs40}True terms, such that she may accept without shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.65,0:36:39.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果她活着 她的盟友都会打着她的旗号\N{\fs40}If she lives, her allies will mass behind her banners,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.53,0:36:41.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,期盼她回来\N{\fs40}looking for her return.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.02,0:36:42.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那她就不能回来\N{\fs40}Then she must not return.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.49,0:36:46.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的丈夫也会希望自己女儿得到宽待\N{\fs40}My husband would have desired this mercy be shown to his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.31,0:36:46.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你丈夫？\N{\fs40}Your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.91,0:36:50.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是你 他女儿的儿时闺蜜？\N{\fs40}Or you, his daughter's childhood companion?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.25,0:36:58.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿·科尔会被任命为御林铁卫队长\N{\fs40}Criston Cole will be named Lord Commander of the Kingsguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.84,0:37:01.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我儿子明日黎明接受涂油礼\N{\fs40}My son will be anointed tomorrow at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.63,0:37:05.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他必须在全君临的见证下登基\N{\fs40}The whole of King's Landing must witness his ascent.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.09,0:37:09.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他要确立权威 事不宜迟\N{\fs40}He will assume authority. There will be no more dithering.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.89,0:37:12.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的儿子与征服者伊耿同名 也将继承他的王冠\N{\fs40}My son will take the crown of his namesake, the Conqueror,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.39,0:37:14.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和他的宝剑黑火\N{\fs40}and carry Blackfyre, his sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.64,0:37:17.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,人们将记起坦格利安家族的古老力量\N{\fs40}Let the people remember the ancient strength of House Targaryen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.03,0:37:25.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在某些方面 你真像你母亲\N{\fs40}You look so much like your mother in certain lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.29,0:37:37.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如你所愿\N{\fs40}As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.43,0:37:51.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs40}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.85,0:37:57.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在已经很晚了 拉里斯大人\N{\fs40}The hour is late, Lord Larys.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.48,0:38:02.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我发现了一件应当告知您的事\N{\fs40}I've found out something that you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.95,0:38:17.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不知道你是否疑心过……\N{\fs40}Have you asked yourself, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.29,0:38:22.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你父亲……国王之手…\N{\fs40}how it is...that your father, the Hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.59,0:38:25.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是怎么先找到伊耿的？\N{\fs40}found Aegon first?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.66,0:39:02.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这红堡中的眼线织就了一张蛛网\N{\fs40}There is a web of spies at work in the Red Keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.50,0:39:06.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,丝线传递着我们的一举一动\N{\fs40}Along its threads travels news of all our doings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.47,0:39:11.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你父亲明知如此 却不予理会\N{\fs40}Your father knows this, but has left it in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.97,0:39:17.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,事实一次次证明 只要你愿意供养织网人\N{\fs40}More than once, it has proved advantageous to those willing to...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.06,0:39:20.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,便可得利\N{\fs40}feed the weaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.73,0:39:23.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而这个织网人在监视我？\N{\fs40}And this weaver watches me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.42,0:39:52.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有只小蜘蛛就是你的侍女\N{\fs40}One of the little spiders is your lady-in-waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.93,0:39:56.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,塔雅？\N{\fs40}Talya?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.61,0:39:57.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,像她这样的还有更多\N{\fs40}There are more like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.85,0:39:59.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,尽管我不知道人数\N{\fs40}Even I do not know their number.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.65,0:40:07.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有个法子可以摧毁他的优势\N{\fs40}There is one way to destroy his advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.90,0:40:11.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,擒贼擒王\N{\fs40}It must be taken out at the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.70,0:40:18.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没了蜂后 蜂群就是一盘散沙\N{\fs40}When the Queen dies, the bees fly without purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.29,0:40:23.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 请原谅我作此比喻\N{\fs40}Begging your pardon for the turn of phrase, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.21,0:40:28.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看来这件事正好是你的专长\N{\fs40}I assume this task falls within your expertise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.67,0:40:30.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只要您有意……\N{\fs40}If you wish it...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.13,0:40:33.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,事会办妥的\N{\fs40}it will be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.55,0:41:54.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让开\N{\fs40}Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.47,0:42:04.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,跟我来 公主\N{\fs40}With me, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.14,0:42:05.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不会纵容如此背信弃义\N{\fs40}I cannot let this treachery stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.31,0:42:47.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们在哪？\N{\fs40}Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.01,0:42:49.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王路南边一点\N{\fs40}Just south of King's Way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.48,0:42:52.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去黑水河走这边\N{\fs40}The Blackwater's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.59,0:43:22.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不能抛下梅丽亚斯\N{\fs40}I won't leave Meleys.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.22,0:43:24.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我能去龙穴的话——\N{\fs40}If I could get to the Dragonpit, then--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.96,0:43:27.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不行 他们料定你会出现在那 公主\N{\fs40}No. They'll expect you there, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.14,0:43:29.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你进不了大门的\N{\fs40}You won't get past the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.94,0:43:31.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs40}Now come.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.35,0:43:33.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你得到河边找艘船\N{\fs40}You must make for the riverfront and find a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.61,0:43:35.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,趁他们还没发觉你走了\N{\fs40}Before they know you've gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.36,0:43:37.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,赶紧 快走\N{\fs40}Move it! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.61,0:43:39.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这边\N{\fs40}This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.24,0:43:41.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就这样 动起来\N{\fs40}Keep moving! That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.78,0:43:43.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\fs40}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.95,0:43:47.12,Note_top,,0,0,0,,继续向前\N{\fs32}Onward!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.95,0:43:47.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这边\N{\fs40}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.20,0:43:49.12,Note_top,,0,0,0,,停！停！\N{\fs32}Halt! Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.67,0:43:53.54,Note_top,,0,0,0,,动起来\N{\fs32}Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.51,0:44:01.05,Note_top,,0,0,0,,所有人 往前走！\N{\fs32}All of you, move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.76,0:44:06.81,Note_top,,0,0,0,,动起来\N{\fs32}Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.19,0:44:19.49,Note_top,,0,0,0,,别挡路\N{\fs32}Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.78,0:44:22.11,Note_top,,0,0,0,,别挡路\N{\fs32}Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.34,0:44:45.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,起码做做样子 感激感激吧\N{\fs40}Have the decency to look grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.68,0:44:49.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你能有今天 知道我做了些什么吗\N{\fs40}Do you know what has been done to give you this day?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.60,0:44:54.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一小时后 你就是国王\N{\fs40}In an hour, you will be king.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.48,0:44:56.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,父亲从来不是这样想的\N{\fs40}And my father never wanted this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.33,0:44:57.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,并不是\N{\fs40}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.36,0:45:00.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,20年来他随时可以指定我作继承人 却从来没有\N{\fs40}He had 20 years to name me heir and never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.53,0:45:02.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他坚定地为雷妮拉的权利撑腰\N{\fs40}Steadfastly, he upheld Rhaenyra's claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.45,0:45:04.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他改了主意\N{\fs40}He changed his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.62,0:45:08.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哇 呵呵 哪有……\N{\fs40}Oh...No...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.20,0:45:12.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他可以 但从来没有\N{\fs40}He could have, but he never did
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.45,0:45:13.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为他不喜欢我\N{\fs40}because he didn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.17,0:45:17.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然而在他临终时\N{\fs40}And yet, with his final breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.54,0:45:20.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还是轻声跟我说 该由你来接替他继承王位\N{\fs40}he whispered to me that you should take his place on the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.07,0:45:43.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别戏弄我了 老妈\N{\fs40}Do not toy with me, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.20,0:45:44.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是真话\N{\fs40}I speak the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.88,0:46:00.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,听着 伊耿\N{\fs40}Listen to me, Aegon.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.34,0:46:03.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你外公 国王之手 会给你灌输观念\N{\fs40}Your grandfather, the Hand, will try to impress on you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.59,0:46:05.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说雷妮拉应该被处死\N{\fs40}that Rhaenyra should be put to the sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.55,0:46:07.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你必须拒绝这一建议\N{\fs40}You must reject this counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.76,0:46:10.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们绝不能靠残暴和冷漠统治\N{\fs40}We must not rule with cruelty and callousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.72,0:46:13.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不管她有什么错 她都是你姐姐 你父亲的女儿——\N{\fs40}For all her faults, she is your sister, your father's daughter--
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.77,0:46:15.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你爱我吗？\N{\fs40}Do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.65,0:46:20.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你个笨蛋\N{\fs40}You imbecile.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.44,0:46:22.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为王家车驾让道\N{\fs40}Make way for the royal wheelhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.17,0:46:41.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 前进啊\N{\fs40}Hey, hey, forward then.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.84,0:46:45.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,继续 动起来 快点\N{\fs40}Go on, move yourself! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.90,0:47:49.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,君临人民\N{\fs40}People of King's Landing...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.57,0:47:52.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今天是最悲伤的一天\N{\fs40}today is the saddest of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.32,0:47:55.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们敬爱的国王\N{\fs40}Our beloved king...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.08,0:47:58.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“安宁王”韦赛里斯\N{\fs40}Viserys the Peaceful...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.08,0:48:01.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,驾崩了\N{\fs40}is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.75,0:48:11.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但今天也是最喜悦的一天\N{\fs40}But it is also the most joyous of days...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.55,0:48:15.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为在他的英灵离开之际\N{\fs40}for as his spirit left us...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.18,0:48:19.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他喃喃道出了遗愿：\N{\fs40}he whispered his final wish:
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.56,0:48:23.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,要由他的长子伊耿……\N{\fs40}that his firstborn son, Aegon...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.11,0:48:27.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,继任王位\N{\fs40}should succeed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.24,0:48:39.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,卫兵\N{\fs40}Guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.04,0:48:43.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让路 闪开\N{\fs40}Out of the way! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.88,0:48:53.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,立正！\N{\fs40}Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.34,0:48:54.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,转身！\N{\fs40}Turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.77,0:49:05.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,举剑……\N{\fs40}Present...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.81,0:49:06.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,行礼！\N{\fs40}arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.47,0:49:42.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,得以见证此刻\N{\fs40}It is your great good fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.72,0:49:46.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,实乃尔等万幸与荣光\N{\fs40}and privilege... to be here to witness this:
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.02,0:49:50.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是城市的新纪元\N{\fs40}a new day for our city...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.57,0:49:54.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,亦是王国的新纪元\N{\fs40}a new day for our realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.44,0:49:58.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,引领我们的新国王\N{\fs40}A new king... to lead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.13,0:51:00.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,愿战士赐勇气于其身\N{\fs40}May the Warrior give him courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.85,0:51:07.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,愿铁匠注力量于其剑盾\N{\fs40}May the Smith lend strength to his sword and shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.60,0:51:12.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,愿天父助其于患难\N{\fs40}May the Father defend him in his need.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.90,0:51:22.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,愿老妪以明灯引其于路途\N{\fs40}May the Crone lift her shining lamp and light his way to wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.43,0:51:50.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,征服者之冠代代相传\N{\fs40}The crown of the Conqueror, passed down through generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.20,0:52:11.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,恭请七神见证\N{\fs40}Let the Seven bear witness:
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.71,0:52:15.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿·坦格利安即铁王座的真正继承人\N{\fs40}Aegon Targaryen is the true heir to the Iron Throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.37,0:52:55.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿二世\N{\fs40}All hail His Grace, Aegon,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.17,0:52:56.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,安达尔人 洛伊拿人\N{\fs40}Second of his Name,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.04,0:53:00.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和先民的国王\N{\fs40}King of the Andals and the Rhoynar and the First Men,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.88,0:53:03.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七国统治者\N{\fs40}Lord of the Seven Kingdoms
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.22,0:53:05.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,暨全境守护者万岁\N{\fs40}and Protector of the Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.10,0:53:10.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿国王！\N{\fs40}Aegon the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.87,0:54:16.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿国王 伊耿国王万岁！\N{\fs40}Aegon the King! Long live Aegon!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.64,0:55:20.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,开门！\N{\fs40}Open the doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.90,0:55:29.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,开门！\N{\fs40}Open the doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.87,0:55:35.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,保护海伦娜\N{\fs40}Get Helaena.
